    "body": "Adding \"ValidStances: Ally\" also to the projectile shouldn't be functionally necessary;\nBoth the Medic & Mechanic have \"TargetStances: Ally\" attached to the actor's \"Armament:\" so the targeting of enemies was never possible.\n\nMEDI:/MECH:\n+Armament:\n++Weapon: Heal/Repair\n++Cursor: heal/repair\n++OutsideRangeCursor: heal/repair\n++**TargetStances: Ally**\n++ForceTargetStances: None\n"
